  "description": "Density at absolute minimum — 0.04. One grain at a time. Large grain size 0.85 so each single grain is a long, sustained fragment. posScatter 1.0 means every grain fires at a completely random position in the source buffer. The pattern is: silence, then a long strange fragment from somewhere unknown, then silence again. No prediction is possible. This is the anti-pad: an instrument that refuses to sustain.",
